detailedRequirements:
Task Overview

The goal of this challenge is to filter posts that are associated with root categories.

Task Requirements

We recently updated csfv forums module to associate not categorized posts with root category of the forum (configured root category). We want to add option in the filter panel called "No Categories" to list these posts.

You are expected to update :

  • Backend Forums.js controller in csfv_forums_module to retrieve posts that are associated with root category when "No Categories" are selected.
  • Add "No Categories" option to first categories filter drop down list in main site and minisites.

Github Code

CSFV websites code exists in private github repository http://github.com/topcoderinc

Here is the repositories (you can search for them in the github.com link provided above) :

  • csfv_frontend_module (this is the main site)
  • csfv_minisite_frontend_module (we have 5 minisites, use branches : minisite1, minisite2, minisite3, minisite4, and minisite5)
  • csfv_forums_module : this is the forums module that contains the forums controllers and models.

Deliverables

  • Patch file of changes.
  • Text file with any note to reviewer.
